- ♪ I wanna be free ♪</i>

22:34.219 --> 22:37.295
<i>♪ Free from the fear in me ♪</i>

22:37.342 --> 22:39.123
<i>You've always been there for me</i>

22:39.157 --> 22:42.393
through thick and thin,
through my successes,

22:42.427 --> 22:44.728
but more importantly my failures.

22:44.763 --> 22:47.131
And I'm not sure

22:47.165 --> 22:49.633
what I would've done without you,

22:49.668 --> 22:52.269
who I would've become without you there,

22:52.304 --> 22:53.837
every step of the way.

22:54.940 --> 22:58.442
But you were there... for every step...

22:58.476 --> 23:02.479
every slip... every time I got up again.

23:02.514 --> 23:06.584
Thank you for this day and
every one that's come before.

23:06.618 --> 23:09.253
I love you so much, Dad.

23:15.060 --> 23:19.050
♪ Those schoolgirl days ♪

23:19.120 --> 23:21.799
♪ Of telling tales ♪

23:21.854 --> 23:27.905
♪ And biting nails are gone ♪

23:29.708 --> 23:33.143
